channel.title: Client loads for me but not other people
channel.description:
I tried to give me Client to my friend i deleted all the .java files and gave it to him but it didn't work, then i gave him it with all the java files in but it still didn't work. When he ran it it just said "Error Loading please report" it didn't even get to the login part.
Any ideas on what i have to do to fix this?
